4. Technologies Used
Programming Language: Python
Libraries:
• Pandas – Data analysis
• NumPy – Numerical calculations
• Matplotlib / Seaborn / Plotly – Visualization
• Streamlit or Dash – Dashboard development
Tools:
• Jupyter Notebook
• VS Code
• GitHub


5. Dataset Information
Dataset includes:
• Battery Capacity (kWh)
• Charge Level (%)
• Distance traveled (km)
• Energy consumption (Wh/km)
• Charging time (minutes)
• Vehicle speed (km/h)
Dataset sources:
• Kaggle EV datasets
• Simulated data


6. System Architecture
Steps:
Data Collection
Data Cleaning
Data Analysis
Visualization
Dashboard Creation

7. Features of the Tool
• Battery charge visualization
• Range prediction graph
• Charging efficiency analysis
• Interactive dashboard
• User-friendly interface
